data.description: Check out this well maintained 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in Alexander. Large backyard and covered patio. Two car garage with keypad entry from the exterior. Nice size master walk in closet.  Eco Friendly with solar panels, Low Monthly Electric Costs. Easy access to the highway and close to Little Rock Outlets, Dining and more. The perfect home for first time homebuyers or Investors looking for a prime rental property. Schedule your home showing today, this will not last long!
